file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  title: warehouse.ai
  version: 7.0.0
  description: Scalable Object Ledger and CDN
definitions: {}
paths:
  /cdn:
    post:
      parameters:
        - required: false
          in: query
          name: expiration
          schema:
            oneOf:
              - type: string
              - type: number
        - required: false
          in: query
          name: cdn_base_url
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        "201":
          description: Default Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  fingerprints:
                    type: array
                    items:
                      type: string
                  recommended:
                    type: array
                    items:
                      type: string
                  files:
                    type: array
                    items:
                      type: object
                      properties:
                        url:
                          type: string
                        metadata:
                          additionalProperties: true
                          nullable: true
                          type: object
  "/objects/{name}":
    get:
      parameters:
        - required: false
          in: query
          name: accepted_variants
          schema:
            type: string
        - required: false
          in: query
          name: version
          schema:
            type: string
        - required: false
          in: query
          name: env
          schema:
            type: string
        - required: true
          in: path
          name: name
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Default Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  type: object
                  properties:
                    name:
                      type: string
                    env:
                      type: string
                    version:
                      type: string
                    data:
                      additionalProperties: true
                      oneOf:
                        - type: string
                        - type: object
                    variant:
                      type: string
  "/head/{name}/{env}":
    get:
      parameters:
        - required: true
          in: path
          name: name
          schema:
            type: string
        - required: true
          in: path
          name: env
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Default Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  headVersion:
                    nullable: true
                    type: string
                  latestVersion:
                    type: string
  /objects:
    post:
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              required:
                - name
                - version
                - data
              properties:
                name:
                  type: string
                version:
                  type: string
                env:
                  type: string
                variant:
                  type: string
                expiration:
                  oneOf:
                    - type: string
                    - type: number
                data:
                  oneOf:
                    - type: object
                    - type: string
      responses:
        "201":
          description: Default Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  created:
                    type: boolean
  "/objects/{name}/{env}":
    delete:
      parameters:
        - required: true
          in: path
          name: name
          schema:
            type: string
        - required: true
          in: path
          name: env
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        "204":
          description: Default Response
    put:
      parameters:
        - required: true
          in: path
          name: name
          schema:
            type: string
        - required: true
          in: path
          name: env
          schema:
            type: string
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              required:
                - head
              properties:
                head:
                  type: string
      responses:
        "204":
          description: Default Response
  "/objects/{name}/{env}/{version}":
    delete:
      parameters:
        - required: false
          in: query
          name: variant
          schema:
            type: string
        - required: true
          in: path
          name: name
          schema:
            type: string
        - required: true
          in: path
          name: env
          schema:
            type: string
        - required: true
          in: path
          name: version
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        "204":
          description: Default Response
  "/objects/{name}/{env}/rollback":
    put:
      parameters:
        - required: true
          in: path
          name: name
          schema:
            type: string
        - required: true
          in: path
          name: env
          schema:
            type: string
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              properties:
                hops:
                  type: number
                  minimum: 1
                  maximum: 20
                  default: 1
      responses:
        "204":
          description: Default Response
  /:
    get:
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Default Response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: string
